overview: Double8Tickets.com is an independent ticket broker, specialising in obtaining tickets in the First 10 rows for most rock and pop concerts in the UK. We pride ourselves on being able to get hold of that very special ticket that everybody wants but no one seems to have!! Of course not all of our tickets are in the First 10 rows - we can obtain a wide selection of tickets for all sold out events, and we can cater to all budgets. Missed an on-sale date? Queued on the phone for hours and still missed out? Don’t want to stress yourself out trying to get those special tickets? Call Double8Tickets.com! We can also supply tickets for sporting events and theatre shows.
